  "purpose": "Written at node entry after the current-node FlowPilot Route Sign has been refreshed, visibly displayed, and the PM has rechecked this node against the run's highest-achievable product target. It turns this node's concrete obligations and inherited root high-risk requirements into experiments, checks, fixtures, and evidence paths before implementation or node closure.",
